Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就好啦 ， 我从未坐过飞机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你等我带手信回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可怜小姐 ， 原来你没有穿内裤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,浴衣下通常都什么也不穿的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.49,0:00:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可怜睡觉时也是不穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿唯 ， 你怎会知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是秘密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很大啊 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.01,0:00:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,空气也很清新
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.28,0:00:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.39,0:00:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点落水吧 ， 阿唯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们两个没事吧 ！ ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:00:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可怜你真顽皮 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.90,0:01:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你问我为何突然去浸温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我稍后自会解释
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.14,0:01:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至于学长的爱情故事有何发展…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,男仔… 真是难以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第 2 乐章
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「 阿实. 友美和温泉旅行 」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,结果…我又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难得来到 ， 不如回学校看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦 ， 阿唯 ， 你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为 ， 我的内裤全都很孩子气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若晾在哥哥会看见的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他会取笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龙之介已经出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他今早才回来罢了 ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直在找那条内裤 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说起来 ， 这条内裤不是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来是妈妈你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我甚至问过哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别为这点事大惊小怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为…那很贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 ， 那不衬你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 ， 哥哥好像喜欢成熟一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看若我也穿那种内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他可能会稍为看上我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但内裤不是让人看的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不管 ！ 那是感觉的问题 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用急 ， 你将来也会变得很美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美得连哥哥也会回头望我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:04:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你放心 ， 要对自己有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三四郎学长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,花朵们好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 ， 因为在放假的期间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会有人来破坏花圃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在我毕业礼送给我的植物图鉴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我现在仍好好保存啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要找个地方晾干这套衫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,学长 ， 有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿 …实 …？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 ， 我是实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当时我说话无礼 ， 真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我以往一直掩饰自己的真正外表
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对别人没信心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我没有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能听我倾诉的只有学长你 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看来能因为一个人而改变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我应该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…我不大清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但重要的是坦诚表白心迹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且 ， 你只好为一直欺骗他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全心全意道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,万一我那样做 ， 他也不原谅我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你只好不断道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直至他肯原谅你为止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,换了是我也会那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你信我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,学长 ， 我会尝试道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会尝试用真面目去面对他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这… ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,学长 ， 我告诉你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回来学校的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定是要穿校服和拿着书包的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很快也要跟这套校服道别了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还一直很喜欢穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其他学校的学生也很喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看 …你穿着校服时…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是不要蹦蹦跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个嘛…喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三四郎学长你真古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说话好像哥哥一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前阵子也说过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你口中的哥哥…即是龙之介？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请你别告诉大家我称呼他为哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,芭菲也好 ， 蛋糕也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,铁板烧也好 ， 我什么也会请你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,否则 ， 哥哥会讨厌我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会 …告诉别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的 ！ ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当 …当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,友美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你别胡来啊 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你放心 ， 我不会拍你的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我只是对你的下身有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停手 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,友…美…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那种事…我不会答应 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么 ， 让龙之介看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,友美 ， 发生什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿唯 ！ 三四郎学长 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有要事…再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,友美 ！ 等…等等 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,学长 ， 我失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿唯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还未干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能只好这样子去兼职了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,友美 ， 你在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 ， 我认错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我记起了 ， 你在便利店…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢…谢谢你送我一程
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没走路来那么难为情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.29,0:08:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么 ， 我失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来她跟我是读同一间学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 ， 没见过她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美雪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道这附近的水野宅在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你妈妈担心你 ，于是 ， 她联络我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她提议你不如学钢琴来松弛一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我小时已经学过弹钢琴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且现在根本没那种时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,友美你无精打采啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你又经常听我倾诉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我无论如何会帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没事 ， 如果我有事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我第一个便会找你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使考试快到也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,休息是必需的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们不如一起去购物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那可能不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那跟钢琴有关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是技术有进步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,钢琴也不会弹得好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为琴声会反映出弹琴者的心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了弹奏出清澈镪锵的乐韵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看消除心中烦恼也是课程之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尽管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还以为冬天没泳衣卖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:10:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认为这样能令人暂时放松一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 ， 就这件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我稍为大胆了 一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,友美你不如也试穿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…我不试了 … ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别那样说 ， 来 ， 不如穿这件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来 ， 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等…等等 ！ 阿唯 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别担心 ， 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,行了 ， 我自己脱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,友美你的身段很美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿唯你才美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 ， 我的臀部很大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不如姐姐你也试穿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不过陪她们来罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别那样说 ， 我看这件很衬你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 …不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只得一条带绑住 ， 我没信心穿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,未试过不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟男人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光是站着看是不能了解他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有时是要我们女性采取主动的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,…友美你毕竟适合穿可爱的款式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三四郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在是你最美好的时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有时你想有那种烦恼的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也未必可以有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就像现在的我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女性谈恋爱时会漂亮起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,男性谈恋爱时则会磨练心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没谈恋爱也就憔悴起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 ， 你有空吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三四郎先生 ， 这件好看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有时也会穿成这样子上街去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…我看现在也很衬你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来帝大也会教人奉承别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我很高兴 ， 让你看件珍藏的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真是很久没穿给别人看了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么人会穿这种内裤呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能衬可怜小姐呢 ， 这么成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定也衬阿唯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没兴趣 ， 因为我不着急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在穿这种已经够
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿唯 ， 美雪老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在这种地方做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我刚刚拍摄完毕离开录影厂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可怜 ， 有好的事情发生了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,何 …何出此言 ！ ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为你看来比平日开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由明天开始 ， 我有一星期假期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来你能放假 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能全靠反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美佐子女士很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 ， 今日始终见不了美雪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们毕竟无缘吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光等是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没法子呢 ， 你这么可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待我给你一次机会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是今次罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先生 ， 如果你要抽奖的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你可以把那张抽奖卷给我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今日很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,间中这样子不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,洋子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一脸天真的样子 ， 没有化妆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.11,0:14:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是 ， 裙子却非常短
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,男仔毕竟会喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿唯你这种女仔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,洋子怎么了 ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你回来喇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈 ， 洋子发生什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是洋子小姐叫我交给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:14:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,温泉旅行招待卷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那好像是阿明送给她的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她说是抽奖抽中的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她为何送给我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她起初提及龙之介 ， 但跟着说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若跟你一起 ，那家伙应该也会去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,于是便留下招待卷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且还是两张
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说起来 ， 她今日好像心不在焉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈 ！ 你那套衫…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 ， 深夜时份打电话给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你约我去浸温泉 ， 我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过是即日来回呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:15:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 ， 我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今日得各位乘坐本公司的巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真的深表谢意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是各位的巴士导游野野村美里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们大约三小时后便会去到温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请各位慢慢欣赏沿途的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三四郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自上次之后 ，我们便没机会见面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美雪小姐 ， 美雪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在想什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不如马上去浸温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不如休息一会吧 ， 大家很倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们两个真是不懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:17:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要浸温泉首先是要换上浴衣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 ， 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们不可当真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好 ！ 还有人留在车上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先生 ， 请你醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经到步了 ， 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 …对不起 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你沿途看来睡得很酣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我没有叫醒你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,绑上一点会比较可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美雪小姐 ， 你不除胸围吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我觉得难为情…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没所谓吧 ， 这里只有女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用拘谨的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:17:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只怪你睡在那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还是快点去露天温泉暖一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我其实现在正打算去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直行到尽头转右就是男温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,左面则是女温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？ 还是相反才对？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算吧 ， 好 ， 我也去暖一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也还保持得不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就好啦 ， 我从未坐过飞机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你等我带手信回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,导游小姐你也来浸温泉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可怜小姐 ， 原来你没有穿内裤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,浴衣下通常都什么也不穿的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可怜睡觉时也是不穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:18:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿唯 ， 你怎会知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:19:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是秘密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我毕竟敌不过青春少艾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的嘴巴很大 ， 看来能放进石头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石头？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,猜拳里的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真懂说笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唯小姐你很有幽默感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我觉得很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若参加相声之类的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看你可能会发挥惊人的才能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿唯 ， 你不如跟我拍档吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎说也好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:19:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还是想弹钢琴和拉小提琴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弹钢琴的话 ， 我随时可以教你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美雪小姐你为何学钢琴？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我其实是别有用心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我小学时非常喜欢一个音乐老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想他称赞我 ，所以开始学钢琴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不如再走入一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们探险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在这里留多一会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,城市的男人全部都是色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不可以一个人去那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈 ！ 你根本不明 白我的心情 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没她办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来这边也这么大 ， 厉害 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是老板娘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请让我们跟你一起浸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请各位慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 …对不起 ， 我还以为无人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好极…我还以为被发现…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在这种地方做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 …喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦 ， 你是刚才那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请你别误会 …我以为是男温泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道因为我指示错误… ！ ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道有人在这里游水？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.31,0:21:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,青春真好呢 ， 拥有美丽的身段
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.11,0:21:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的皮肤也很滑溜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别…别说笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你从未给男人摸过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光是封闭心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是无法开展一段恋情的 ， 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发生什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.87,0:22:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道他想偷窥 ！ ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…不是 ， 他有苦衷的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三四郎学长 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.82,0:22:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我为何会在这里 ！ ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.52,0:22:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听闻你在温泉热到晕倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.13,0:22:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 ， 你看来没事 ， 我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.53,0:22:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当日我担心得无法入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.10,0:22:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.37,0:22:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你当日有给那个人打伤吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只怪我不懂打架
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.71,0:22:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不懂打架还要为我… ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.81,0:22:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很高兴 ， 以前那个人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:22:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没想过我能在这种地方见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.45,0:23:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我觉得好像是命运的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.12,0:23:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…那么 ， 我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.89,0:23:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三四郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你认为温柔待人是什么一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你…你为何突然那样问？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为温柔待一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.73,0:23:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就想对方亦温柔待自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.24,0:23:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又或者是因为想对方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.34,0:23:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,认为自己是个温柔的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.91,0:23:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而想对方认为自己温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是因为想对方喜欢自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么 ， 温柔不过是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.31,0:23:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用来欺骗对方的手段吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.92,0:23:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美雪小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认为牺牲自己也不求回报的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.16,0:23:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才算真正的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.26,0:23:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但那种东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.96,0:23:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 …对不起 ！ 我只顾自说自话 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.30,0:23:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可以迟些才答你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.57,0:23:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在的我不知道那问题的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.94,0:23:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以 ， 我会去找 ，我一定会找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.84,0:23:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是… ！ 我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.21,0:23:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.94,0:23:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可以入来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.15,0:24:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…我再去浸多一次温泉 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.62,0:24:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,学长 ， 好极了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.02,0:24:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在我过往的恋情和人生里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.59,0:24:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直只是尝到痛苦和悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.36,0:24:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,友美 ， 一个人无论任何时候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.67,0:24:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或多或少都会怀有悲伤的心事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.43,0:24:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为那才是生存的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.37,0:24:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重要的是如何去面对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.64,0:24:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有不逃避. 勇敢面对的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.81,0:24:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才能经常面带笑容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.81,0:24:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.15,0:24:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 ， 我一无所知却口出狂言
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.52,0:24:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我见你无精打采 ， 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.39,0:24:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全靠你 ， 我没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.39,0:24:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,学长 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.69,0:24:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请你不要再吓我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.89,0:24:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,学长 ， 你为何会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.16,0:24:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道你追着来？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.36,0:24:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…不是啊 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.80,0:24:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我抽奖赢得招待卷啊 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.00,0:24:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抽奖？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.54,0:25:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,浸温泉真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.02,0:25:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回去后 ， 你可以教我弹钢琴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.33,0:25:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.23,0:25:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我现在看来能弹出悠扬乐韵
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.50,0:25:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说起来 ， 你看来很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.63,0:25:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那全靠三四郎学长
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.70,0:25:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,学长的一番话令我轻松了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.97,0:25:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三四郎先生他…？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.51,0:25:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会再逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.31,0:25:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要令他察觉他是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.48,0:25:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.71,0:25:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三四郎学长是个不可思议的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.15,0:25:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我觉得他的每一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.85,0:25:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都能令人感到无比的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.23,0:25:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有一件事不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.53,0:26:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.30,0:26:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美雪小姐 ， 若你不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.77,0:26:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们下次不如单独见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.10,0:26:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也有些话想跟三四郎先生你说
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.54,0:26:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一月三日 ， 二时
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.21,0:26:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们在八十八公园见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.25,0:26:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.81,0:26:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想知道多一些你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.75,0:26:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好极了呢 ， 学长
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.59,0:26:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,温泉的事我会替你保守秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.92,0:26:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请你快点忘记我的裸体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.19,0:26:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一言为定啊
